sort an array of 0's and 1's and 2's.

arr[]={0,1,2,0,1,2,1,0,0,0,1}
1-Brute force-

count 0=5
count 1=4
count 2=3

for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
  if(a[i]==0) count0++;
else if(arr[i]==1) count1++;
else count2++;
}
for(i=0;i<count0;i++) a[i]=0
for(i=count0;i<count0+count1;i++) arr[i]=1;
for(i=count0+count1;i<n;i++) arr[i]=2;

